<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Mehndi Night | FIORE</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
   <!-- AOS Library CDN -->
   <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>

   <!-- AOS Library JS -->
   <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>
   <script>
     AOS.init({
       duration: 2500,  // Animation lasts for 2500 milliseconds
       delay: 300,      // Delay animation by 300 milliseconds before it starts
       once: true       // Ensures animations run only once (when scrolling down) 
     });
   </script>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="mehndi-hero-section">
    <div class="mehndi-hero-text">
      <h1>Mehndi Night</h1>
      <p>A night of color, culture, and celebration</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Intro Section -->
  <section class="mehndi-intro-section" data-aos="fade-up"> 
    <p>
      Mehndi Night, also known as Henna Night, is a vibrant pre-wedding celebration rooted in South Asian traditions. This cultural event is centered around applying intricate henna designs on the bride's hands and feet while guests enjoy music, dancing, and festivities. It's a joyful, women-focused gathering where laughter, elegance, and tradition blend beautifully. Beyond the beauty, henna symbolizes blessings, happiness, and good fortune for the bride’s new journey.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Cards Section -->
  <section class="mehndi-wrapper">
    <div class="mehndi-cards-section">

      <!-- Card 1: Henna Designs -->
      <div class="mehndi-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <img src="/img/mn-img1.png" alt="Henna Application">
        <div class="mehndi-card-content">
          <h2>Intricate Henna Art</h2>
          <p>Skilled henna artists apply traditional and modern designs on the bride and guests, believed to bring love and prosperity. The deeper the color, the stronger the bond!
          <a href="/henna-designers" class="luxury-button">Explore Designs</a>
          </p>
        </div>
       </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Music & Dance -->
      <div class="mehndi-card" data-aos="zoom-out">
        <img src="/img/mn-dance.jpg" alt="Mehndi Night Dance">
        <div class="mehndi-card-content">
          <h2>Music & Dance</h2>
          <p>Family and friends prepare dance performances, traditional songs are sung, and the atmosphere becomes alive with dhol beats and laughter-filled moves.
          <a href="/dancing_groups_girls" class="luxury-button">Dancing academies</a>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Decor & Vibe -->
      <div class="mehndi-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <img src="/img/mn-decor.png" alt="Mehndi Night Decor">
        <div class="mehndi-card-content">
          <h2>Colorful Decor</h2>
          <p>The venue is adorned with vibrant fabrics, marigold flowers, fairy lights, and cushions, creating a dreamy and joyful ambiance that sets the tone for celebration.
          <a href="/decorators" class="luxury-button">Explore decorators</a>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 4: Traditional Outfits -->
      <div class="mehndi-card" data-aos="zoom-out">
        <img src="/img/mn-dress2.jpeg" alt="Traditional Mehndi Outfit">
        <div class="mehndi-card-content">
          <h2>Ethnic Fashion</h2>
          <p>The bride wears bright, embellished outfits—often green or yellow. Guests wear colorful traditional attire, adding to the cultural richness of the evening.
          <br><br>
          <a href="/dresses" class="luxury-button">Explore Dresspoints</a>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 5: Rituals & Blessings -->
      <div class="mehndi-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
        <img src="/img/mn2.png" alt="Rituals and Blessings">
        <div class="mehndi-card-content">
          <h2>Rituals & Blessings</h2>
          <p>Relatives bless the bride with sweets, gifts, and well wishes. These rituals strengthen family bonds and carry deep symbolic meaning in preparing the bride for married life.
          <br>
          <a href="/mehndi_traditions" class="luxury-button">Explore traditions</a>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 6: Traditional indian dinner -->
      <div class="mehndi-card" data-aos="zoom-out">
        <img src="/img/mn-dinner.png" alt="Traditional indian dinner">
        <div class="mehndi-card-content">
          <h2>Traditional Indian Dinner</h2>
          <p>Savor the rich flavors of India with a delightful spread of aromatic biryanis, spicy curries, fresh naan, and sweet desserts — a feast to celebrate love, tradition, and togetherness.
          <br><br>
          <a href="/catering_services" class="luxury-button">Catering services</a>
        </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
